# No Cursor attribution

- Never add `Co-authored-by: Cursor` or any Cursor/agent attribution to commit messages, tags, changelogs, or release notes.
- Commits should only list human authors for this project.
- When creating git commits, use a clean message with no co-author trailers unless the user explicitly names a real person.
